Flowing Wells JROTC Rifle Team just qualified for the National JROTC Championship at Camp Perry, Ohio(19-21MAR 2020).Teams participated from all 50 states, the Pacific, and Europe. Each service(Army, Navy, Air Force, and Marine Corps) can only send seven teams to National, for the Army JROTC there were over 1600 teams, and Flowing Wells was number seven. Below is the team that's going to the Nationals. Please congratulate the team if you see them. Way to go, Cabs!

Casey Downing
Kaitlyn Rendon
Kaitlyn Martin(Ironwood Ridge HS)
Israel Martinez- Team Captain
Tristan Konigsfeld
Coach: Vincent Tolliver
